Name: Chuck 70 High Tops
Description: The Converse All Star Chuck ’70 is our re-crafted sneaker that uses modern details to celebrate the original Chuck Taylor All Star from the 1970's. It features a slightly higher rubber foxing, a cushioned footbed that provides long-lasting comfort and a more substantial rubber toe cap. Additional vintage details include stitching on the sidewall and a heavier-grade canvas upper for comfort and durability. It’s an authentic throwback look that retains the iconic Chuck Taylor attributes you know and love, like the star-centered ankle patch and vulcanized rubber outsole.
